725452f-a.title: Queens: 54th Avenue - Maurice Avenue
725452f-a.text:
Fifty-fourth Ave. (Newtown Ave., tracks thereon), at the S.W.
corner of Maurice Ave., showing the old Scudder farmhouse. Other
owners of this house were James Way from 1852 to 1860; H.F. Way from
1860-1873. This house stood formerly on the N.W. corner of the above
mentioned streets in what is today a part of Mt. 2ion Cemetery.
March 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
